vernac_cmds: Fixpoint naryFunc (A : Set) (n : nat) {struct n} : Set := match n with | O => A | S m => A -> naryFunc A m end.
Fixpoint naryRel (A : Set) (n : nat) {struct n} : Type := match n with | O => Prop | S m => A -> naryRel A m end.
Record Model : Type := model {U : Set; func : forall f : Functions L, naryFunc U (arity L (inr _ f)); rel : forall r : Relations L, naryRel U (arity L (inl _ r))}.

Fixpoint interpTerm (value : nat -> U M) (t : Term L) {struct t} : U M := match t with | var v => value v | apply f ts => interpTerms _ (func M f) value ts end with interpTerms (m : nat) (f : naryFunc (U M) m) (value : nat -> U M) (ts : Terms L m) {struct ts} : U M := match ts in (Terms _ n) return (naryFunc (U M) n -> U M) with | Tnil => fun f => f | Tcons m t ts => fun f => interpTerms m (f (interpTerm value t)) value ts end f.

Fixpoint interpRels (m : nat) (r : naryRel (U M) m) (value : nat -> U M) (ts : Terms L m) {struct ts} : Prop := match ts in (Terms _ n) return (naryRel (U M) n -> Prop) with | Tnil => fun r => r | Tcons m t ts => fun r => interpRels m (r (interpTerm value t)) value ts end r.
Definition updateValue (value : nat -> U M) (n : nat) (v : U M) (x : nat) : U M := match eq_nat_dec n x with | left _ => v | right _ => value x end.

Fixpoint interpFormula (value : nat -> U M) (f : Formula L) {struct f} : Prop := match f with | equal t s => interpTerm value t = interpTerm value s | atomic r ts => interpRels _ (rel M r) value ts | impH A B => interpFormula value A -> interpFormula value B | notH A => interpFormula value A -> False | forallH v A => forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue value v x) A end.
Lemma freeVarInterpTerm : forall (v1 v2 : nat -> U M) (t : Term L), (forall x : nat, In x (freeVarTerm L t) -> v1 x = v2 x) -> interpTerm v1 t = interpTerm v2 t.

elim t using Term_Terms_ind with (P0 := fun (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) => forall f : naryFunc (U M) n, (forall x : nat, In x (freeVarTerms L n ts) -> v1 x = v2 x) -> interpTerms n f v1 ts = interpTerms n f v2 ts); simpl in |- *; intros.

Lemma freeVarInterpRel : forall (v1 v2 : nat -> U M) (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) (r : naryRel (U M) n), (forall x : nat, In x (freeVarTerms L n ts) -> v1 x = v2 x) -> interpRels n r v1 ts -> interpRels n r v2 ts.
intros v1 v2 n ts r H.
induction ts as [| n t ts Hrects]; simpl in |- *.
Lemma freeVarInterpFormula : forall (v1 v2 : nat -> U M) (g : Formula L), (forall x : nat, In x (freeVarFormula L g) -> v1 x = v2 x) -> interpFormula v1 g -> interpFormula v2 g.
induction g as [t t0| r t| g1 Hrecg1 g0 Hrecg0| g Hrecg| n g Hrecg]; simpl in |- *; intros v1 v2 H.
assert (interpFormula v2 g1 -> interpFormula v1 g1).
assert (interpFormula v1 g0 -> interpFormula v2 g0).
apply Hrecg with (updateValue v1 n x).
Lemma subInterpTerm : forall (value : nat -> U M) (t : Term L) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpTerm (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) t = interpTerm value (substituteTerm L t v s).

elim t using Term_Terms_ind with (P0 := fun (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) => forall f : naryFunc (U M) n, interpTerms n f (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) ts = interpTerms n f value (substituteTerms L n ts v s)); simpl in |- *; intros.

Lemma subInterpRel : forall (value : nat -> U M) (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) (v : nat) (s : Term L) (r : naryRel (U M) n), interpRels n r (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) ts <-> interpRels n r value (substituteTerms L n ts v s).
induction ts as [| n t ts Hrects].

Lemma subInterpFormula : forall (value : nat -> U M) (f : Formula L) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f <-> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f v s).
elim f using Formula_depth_ind2; simpl in |- *; intros.
assert (interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f1 <-> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f1 v s)).
assert (interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f0 <-> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f0 v s)).
assert (interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f0 <-> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f0 v s)).
apply freeVarInterpFormula with (fun x0 : nat => match eq_nat_dec v0 x0 with | left _ => x | right _ => match eq_nat_dec v0 x0 with | left _ => interpTerm value s | right _ => value x0 end end).
apply freeVarInterpFormula with (fun x0 : nat => match eq_nat_dec v0 x0 with | left _ => x | right _ => value x0 end).
set (nv := newVar (v0 :: freeVarTerm L s ++ freeVarFormula L a)) in *.
assert (~ In nv (v0 :: freeVarTerm L s ++ freeVarFormula L a)).

assert (forall (x : U M) (x0 : nat), In x0 (freeVarFormula L a) -> updateValue (updateValue value v0 (interpTerm value s)) v x x0 = updateValue (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) v (interpTerm (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) (var L nv)) x0).

assert ((forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) v (interpTerm (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) (var L nv))) a) <-> (forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue value nv x) (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (var L nv)) v0 s))).

assert (forall b : Formula L, lt_depth L b (forallH L v a) -> forall (value : nat -> U M) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) b -> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L b v s)).
induction (H b0 H2 value0 v1 s0).

assert (forall b : Formula L, lt_depth L b (forallH L v a) -> forall (value : nat -> U M) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula value (substituteFormula L b v s) -> interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) b).
induction (H b0 H3 value0 v1 s0).

assert ((forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue (updateValue value v0 (interpTerm value s)) v x) a) <-> (forall x : U M, interpFormula (updateValue (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) v (interpTerm (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) (var L nv))) a)).
apply freeVarInterpFormula with (updateValue (updateValue value v0 (interpTerm value s)) v x).

apply freeVarInterpFormula with (updateValue (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) v (interpTerm (updateValue (updateValue value nv x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value nv x) s)) (var L nv))).

assert (forall (x : U M) (x0 : nat), In x0 (freeVarFormula L a) -> updateValue (updateValue value v0 (interpTerm value s)) v x x0 = updateValue (updateValue value v x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value v x) s) x0).

assert (forall b : Formula L, lt_depth L b (forallH L v a) -> forall (value : nat -> U M) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) b -> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L b v s)).
induction (H b1 H2 value0 v1 s0).
apply freeVarInterpFormula with (updateValue (updateValue value v0 (interpTerm value s)) v x).

assert (forall b : Formula L, lt_depth L b (forallH L v a) -> forall (value : nat -> U M) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula value (substituteFormula L b v s) -> interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) b).
induction (H b1 H1 value0 v1 s0).
apply freeVarInterpFormula with (updateValue (updateValue value v x) v0 (interpTerm (updateValue value v x) s)).

Lemma subInterpFormula1 : forall (value : nat -> U M) (f : Formula L) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f -> interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f v s).

Lemma subInterpFormula2 : forall (value : nat -> U M) (f : Formula L) (v : nat) (s : Term L), interpFormula value (substituteFormula L f v s) -> interpFormula (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) f.

Fixpoint nnHelp (f : Formula L) : Formula L := match f with | equal t s => equal L t s | atomic r ts => atomic L r ts | impH A B => impH L (nnHelp A) (nnHelp B) | notH A => notH L (nnHelp A) | forallH v A => forallH L v (notH L (notH L (nnHelp A))) end.
Definition nnTranslate (f : Formula L) : Formula L := notH L (notH L (nnHelp f)).
Lemma freeVarNNHelp : forall f : Formula L, freeVarFormula L f = freeVarFormula L (nnHelp f).
induction f as [t t0| r t| f1 Hrecf1 f0 Hrecf0| f Hrecf| n f Hrecf]; try reflexivity.
Lemma subNNHelp : forall (f : Formula L) (v : nat) (s : Term L), substituteFormula L (nnHelp f) v s = nnHelp (substituteFormula L f v s).
elim f using Formula_depth_ind2; intros; try reflexivity.

Fixpoint interpTermsVector (value : nat -> U M) (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) {struct ts} : Vector.t (U M) n := match ts in (Terms _ n) return (Vector.t (U M) n) with | Tnil => Vector.nil (U M) | Tcons m t ts => Vector.cons (U M) (interpTerm value t) m (interpTermsVector value m ts) end.
Lemma preserveValue : forall value : nat -> U M, (forall f : Formula L, mem _ T f -> interpFormula value (nnTranslate f)) -> forall g : Formula L, SysPrf L T g -> interpFormula value (nnTranslate g).
cut (forall g : Formula L, In g x -> interpFormula value (nnTranslate g)).
induction x0 as [A| Axm1 Axm2 A B x0_1 Hrecx0_1 x0_0 Hrecx0_0| Axm A v n x0 Hrecx0| A B| A B C| A B| A v t| A v n| A B v| | | | R| f]; intros; try (simpl in |- *; tauto).
induction Axm as [| a0 Axm HrecAxm].
cut (forall a b : Terms L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)), interpTermsVector value _ a = interpTermsVector value _ b -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (iffH L (atomic L R a) (atomic L R b)))).

assert (forall A, (forall a b : Terms L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)), interpTermsVector value (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)) a = interpTermsVector value (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)) b -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (A a b))) -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (nat_rec (fun _ : nat => Formula L) (prod_rec (fun _ : Terms L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)) * Terms L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)) => Formula L) (fun a b : Terms L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)) => A a b) (nVars L (arity L (inl (Functions L) R)))) (fun (n : nat) (Hrecn : Formula L) => impH L (equal L (var L (n + n)) (var L (S (n + n)))) Hrecn) (arity L (inl (Functions L) R))))).
apply (H (fun x y : Terms L n0 => A (Tcons L n0 (var L (n0 + n0)) x) (Tcons L n0 (var L (S (n0 + n0))) y))).
apply (H (fun a b => iffH L (atomic L R a) (atomic L R b))).
induction a as [| n t a Hreca].
cut (forall a b : Terms L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)), interpTermsVector value _ a = interpTermsVector value _ b -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (equal L (apply L f a) (apply L f b)))).

assert (forall A, (forall a b : Terms L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)), interpTermsVector value (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) a = interpTermsVector value (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) b -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (A a b))) -> interpFormula value (nnHelp (nat_rec (fun _ : nat => Formula L) (prod_rec (fun _ : Terms L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) * Terms L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) => Formula L) (fun a b : Terms L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) => A a b) (nVars L (arity L (inr (Relations L) f)))) (fun (n : nat) (Hrecn : Formula L) => impH L (equal L (var L (n + n)) (var L (S (n + n)))) Hrecn) (arity L (inr (Relations L) f))))).
apply (H (fun x y : Terms L n0 => A (Tcons L n0 (var L (n0 + n0)) x) (Tcons L n0 (var L (S (n0 + n0))) y))).
apply (H (fun a b => equal L (apply L f a) (apply L f b))).
induction a as [| n t a Hreca].
Lemma ModelConsistent : forall value : nat -> U M, (forall f : Formula L, mem _ T f -> interpFormula value (nnTranslate f)) -> Consistent L T.
assert (interpFormula value (nnTranslate (notH L (equal L (var L 0) (var L 0))))).

command: elim t using Term_Terms_ind with (P0 := fun (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) => forall f : naryFunc (U M) n, (forall x : nat, In x (freeVarTerms L n ts) -> v1 x = v2 x) -> interpTerms n f v1 ts = interpTerms n f v2 ts); simpl in |- *; intros.
intros v1 v2 n ts r H.
induction ts as [| n t ts Hrects]; simpl in |- *.
induction g as [t t0| r t| g1 Hrecg1 g0 Hrecg0| g Hrecg| n g Hrecg]; simpl in |- *; intros v1 v2 H.
assert (interpFormula v2 g1 -> interpFormula v1 g1).
assert (interpFormula v1 g0 -> interpFormula v2 g0).
apply Hrecg with (updateValue v1 n x).

elim t using Term_Terms_ind with (P0 := fun (n : nat) (ts : Terms L n) => forall f : naryFunc (U M) n, interpTerms n f (updateValue value v (interpTerm value s)) ts = interpTerms n f value (substituteTerms L n ts v s)); simpl in |- *; intros.
induction ts as [| n t ts Hrects].
induction f as [t t0| r t| f1 Hrecf1 f0 Hrecf0| f Hrecf| n f Hrecf]; try reflexivity.
assert (interpFormula value (nnTranslate (notH L (equal L (var L 0) (var L 0))))).
